summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Blocks 64 through 113, Seattle Tidelands; Block 1, 2, 4, 7 and 10, Minor's Addition; and a 100 ft. strip of land extending from Block 94, Seattle Tidelands to 32nd Ave. W.; with respect to Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended by adding thereto one new section numbered 17-271.
